sentences: Suara (すあら) (born Akiko Tatsumi (巽 明子, Tatsumi Akiko) August 3, 1979, in Osaka) is a female Japanese singer working under the FIX Records label, distributed by King Records.
She married composer and arranger Junpei Fujita in 2009.
